headline: Is It Time To Reassess TransDigm Group (TDG) After The Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: If you are wondering whether TransDigm Group's current share price reflects its underlying value, you are not alone. This article is built to help you frame that question clearly. The stock last closed at US$1,295.12, with returns of a 1.5% decline over 7 days, a 9.8% decline over 30 days, a 4.7% decline year to date, but a 3.9% gain over 1 year, 101.8% over 3 years and 164.1% over 5 years that may influence how investors think about both upside and risk today.
